nodes.text: Star Wars Insider 170 is the 148th issue of the Star Wars Insider magazine and the seventy-eighth published by Titan Magazines. Released on December 16, 2016, it includes the short story "The Voice of the Empire."
Behind-the-scenes special on the latest movie! Cast and crew interviews! And don't miss the latest news on Star Wars comics, books, toys and collectibles!
